tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    company_name VARCHAR(255),
    revenue DECIMAL(10,2),
    expenses DECIMAL(10,2),
    profit DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE market_trends (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    trend VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    indicator VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    sentiment VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    amount DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE financial_trends (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    trend_name VARCHAR(50),
    trend_score INT
)

CREATE TABLE opportunities (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    opportunity_name VARCHAR(50),
    opportunity_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE predictions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    prediction_type VARCHAR(50),
    prediction_value DECIMAL
)
